        {
            "id": "https://wangjiosw.github.io/2020/10/22/bigdata/hive/hive-Sougou/",
            "url": "https://wangjiosw.github.io/2020/10/22/bigdata/hive/hive-Sougou/",
            "title": "Hive分析搜狗用户搜索日志-数据预处理",
            "date_published": "2020-10-22T11:34:00.000Z",
            "content_html": "<h1 id=\"环境\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#环境\">#</a> 环境</h1>\n<ul>\n<li>MacOS</li>\n<li>单机 hadoop 集群</li>\n<li>Hive (内嵌模式)</li>\n</ul>\n<h1 id=\"预处理\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#预处理\">#</a> 预处理</h1>\n<h2 id=\"1-查看数据\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#1-查看数据\">#</a> 1. 查看数据</h2>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">head Sougou.reduced</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>结果如下<br>\n<img src=\"/images/bigdata/hive/sougou/origin.png\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p>可以发现有许多乱码</p>\n<h2 id=\"2-查看文件编码\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#2-查看文件编码\">#</a> 2. 查看文件编码</h2>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">file Sougou.reduced</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>结果如下<br>\n<img src=\"/images/bigdata/hive/sougou/file.png\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p>网上查询得知 Non-ISO extended-ASCII text 代表 gb18030</p>\n<h2 id=\"3-使用iconv转换文件编码格式\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#3-使用iconv转换文件编码格式\">#</a> 3. 使用 iconv 转换文件编码格式</h2>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">iconv -f gb18030 -t utf-8 SogouQ.reduced&gt;SogouQ.reduced.new</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>结果如下<br>\n<img src=\"/images/bigdata/hive/sougou/conv.png\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<!-- ## 4. 将文件中的空格和制表符全部替换为英文逗号\n```\nsed -i \"\" \"s/\\t/,/g\" SogouQ.reduced.new\nsed -i \"\" \"s/ /,/g\" SogouQ.reduced.new\n``` -->\n",
            "tags": [
                "macos",
                "hive"
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "https://wangjiosw.github.io/2020/10/21/bigdata/mapreduce/mac-hadoop-jar-problem/",
            "url": "https://wangjiosw.github.io/2020/10/21/bigdata/mapreduce/mac-hadoop-jar-problem/",
            "title": "Mac 单机集群使用hadoop jar 运行jar包出现的问题",
            "date_published": "2020-10-21T03:19:00.000Z",
            "content_html": "<h1 id=\"1-问题描述\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#1-问题描述\">#</a> 1. 问题描述</h1>\n<p>Mac 单机集群使用 hadoop jar 运行 jar 包报错：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">Exception in thread &quot;main&quot; java.io.IOException: Mkdirs failed to create /var/folders/zz/zyxvpxvq6csfxvn_n0000000000000/T/hadoop-unjar7560830407203462827/META-INF/license</span><br><span class=\"line\">at org.apache.hadoop.util.RunJar.ensureDirectory(RunJar.java:128)</span><br><span class=\"line\">at org.apache.hadoop.util.RunJar.unJar(RunJar.java:104)</span><br><span class=\"line\">at org.apache.hadoop.util.RunJar.unJar(RunJar.java:81)</span><br><span class=\"line\">at org.apache.hadoop.util.RunJar.run(RunJar.java:209)</span><br><span class=\"line\">at org.apache.hadoop.util.RunJar.main(RunJar.java:136)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h1 id=\"2-解决方法\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#2-解决方法\">#</a> 2. 解决方法</h1>\n<p>Only thrown in MacOS, and solution is:<br>\n@see: <a href=\"http://stackoverflow.com/questions/10522835/hadoop-java-io-ioexception-mkdirs-failed-to-create-some-path\">http://stackoverflow.com/questions/10522835/hadoop-java-io-ioexception-mkdirs-failed-to-create-some-path</a></p>\n<ol>\n<li>modify jar</li>\n</ol>\n<figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">$</span><span class=\"bash\"> zip -d mipr-core-0.1-jar-with-dependencies.jar META-INF/LICENSE</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">$</span><span class=\"bash\"> zip -d mipr-core-0.1-jar-with-dependencies.jar LICENSE</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ol start=\"2\">\n<li>with grep all</li>\n</ol>\n<figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">$</span><span class=\"bash\"> jar -tvf mipr-core-0.1-jar-with-dependencies.jar |grep META-INF/LICENSE</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>",
            "tags": [
                "macos",
                "mapreduce"
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "https://wangjiosw.github.io/2020/03/17/bigdata/mapreduce/%E6%9C%AC%E5%9C%B0%E8%BF%90%E8%A1%8Cmapred%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98/",
            "url": "https://wangjiosw.github.io/2020/03/17/bigdata/mapreduce/%E6%9C%AC%E5%9C%B0%E8%BF%90%E8%A1%8Cmapred%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98/",
            "title": "本地运行mapred问题",
            "date_published": "2020-03-17T06:58:00.000Z",
            "content_html": "<h1 id=\"1-问题描述\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#1-问题描述\">#</a> 1. 问题描述</h1>\n<p>在 hadoop 集群上跑 mapreduce 代码很慢，可以通过设置</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">conf.set(&quot;mapreduce.framework.name&quot;, &quot;local&quot;);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>使 mapreduce 代码能在本地运行。</p>\n<p>运行时报以下错误：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight java\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"number\">2020</span>-<span class=\"number\">03</span>-<span class=\"number\">14</span> <span class=\"number\">20</span>:<span class=\"number\">24</span>:<span class=\"number\">30</span>,<span class=\"number\">241</span> WARN  [main] util.NativeCodeLoader (NativeCodeLoader.java:&lt;clinit&gt;(<span class=\"number\">62</span>)) - Unable to load <span class=\"keyword\">native</span>-hadoop library <span class=\"keyword\">for</span> your platform... using builtin-java classes where applicable</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"number\">2020</span>-<span class=\"number\">03</span>-<span class=\"number\">14</span> <span class=\"number\">20</span>:<span class=\"number\">24</span>:<span class=\"number\">31</span>,<span class=\"number\">625</span> INFO  [main] Configuration.deprecation (Configuration.java:warnOnceIfDeprecated(<span class=\"number\">1129</span>)) - session.id is deprecated. Instead, use dfs.metrics.session-id</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"number\">2020</span>-<span class=\"number\">03</span>-<span class=\"number\">14</span> <span class=\"number\">20</span>:<span class=\"number\">24</span>:<span class=\"number\">31</span>,<span class=\"number\">626</span> INFO  [main] jvm.JvmMetrics (JvmMetrics.java:init(<span class=\"number\">76</span>)) - Initializing JVM Metrics with processName=JobTracker, sessionId=</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"number\">2020</span>-<span class=\"number\">03</span>-<span class=\"number\">14</span> <span class=\"number\">20</span>:<span class=\"number\">24</span>:<span class=\"number\">31</span>,<span class=\"number\">924</span> WARN  [main] mapreduce.JobResourceUploader (JobResourceUploader.java:uploadFiles(<span class=\"number\">64</span>)) - Hadoop command-line option parsing not performed. Implement the Tool <span class=\"class\"><span class=\"keyword\">interface</span> <span class=\"title\">and</span> <span class=\"title\">execute</span> <span class=\"title\">your</span> <span class=\"title\">application</span> <span class=\"title\">with</span> <span class=\"title\">ToolRunner</span> <span class=\"title\">to</span> <span class=\"title\">remedy</span> <span class=\"title\">this</span>.</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">2020-03-14 20:24:31,948 INFO  [main] mapreduce.JobSubmitter (JobSubmitter.java:submitJobInternal(250)) - Cleaning up the staging area file:/var/sxt/hadoop/ha/mapred/staging/wangji241520974/.staging/job_local241520974_0001</span><br><span class=\"line\">ExitCodeException exitCode=<span class=\"number\">1</span>: chmod: /<span class=\"keyword\">private</span>/<span class=\"keyword\">var</span>/sxt/hadoop/ha/mapred/staging/wangji241520974/.staging/job_local241520974_0001: No such file or directory</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h1 id=\"2-解决方法\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#2-解决方法\">#</a> 2. 解决方法</h1>\n<p>在 /private/var 目录下创建 sxt 目录，并把权限改为 777</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">sudo mkdir sxt</span><br><span class=\"line\">sudo chmod 777 sxt</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>",
            "tags": [
                "macos",
                "hadoop",
                "mapreduce",
                "java"
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "https://wangjiosw.github.io/2020/02/29/bigdata/environment/vmware/",
            "url": "https://wangjiosw.github.io/2020/02/29/bigdata/environment/vmware/",
            "title": "Mac OS VMware Fusion Centos6.5虚拟机网络设置",
            "date_published": "2020-02-29T15:25:00.000Z",
            "content_html": "<h1 id=\"1-安装vmware虚拟机\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#1-安装vmware虚拟机\">#</a> 1. 安装 vmware 虚拟机</h1>\n<p>安装 vmware 虚拟机，并新建一个 centos 64 位的虚拟机</p>\n<h1 id=\"2-设置虚拟机网络模式\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#2-设置虚拟机网络模式\">#</a> 2. 设置虚拟机网络模式</h1>\n<p><img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20200210222413551.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L0pXb3N3aW4=,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<h1 id=\"3-查看vmware的网关和掩码\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#3-查看vmware的网关和掩码\">#</a> 3. 查看 vmware 的网关和掩码</h1>\n<p>在 Mac 电脑的终端输入：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">cat /Library/Preferences/VMware\\ Fusion/vmnet8/nat.conf</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>输出结果如下：<br>\n<img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20200210222624261.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L0pXb3N3aW4=,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70\" alt=\"\"><br>\n这里的 ip 和 netmask 即为 vmware 虚拟机的网关和掩码</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># NAT gateway address</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">ip = 172.16.143.2</span><br><span class=\"line\">netmask = 255.255.255.0</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>ip 和 netmask 后面配置 centos 虚拟机的网络时分别对于网关和掩码。</p>\n<h1 id=\"4-配置centos虚拟机的网络\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#4-配置centos虚拟机的网络\">#</a> 4. 配置 centos 虚拟机的网络</h1>\n<p>在 centos 虚拟机的终端输入：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">vi /etc/sysconfig/network-scripts/ifcfg-eth0</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>然后：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>删除 UUID 和 MAC 地址</li>\n<li>ONBOOT=yes</li>\n<li>BOOTPROTO=static</li>\n<li>IPADDR=172.16.143.101</li>\n<li>NETMASK=255.255.255.0</li>\n<li>GATEWAY=172.16.143.2</li>\n<li>DNS1=172.16.143.2</li>\n</ul>\n<p>保存并退出，然后在 centos 虚拟机的终端输入：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">service network restart</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>ping 一下百度看是否能 ping 通：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">ping www.baidu.com</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>",
            "tags": [
                "vmware",
                "macos"
            ]
        }
    ]
}